n: Paleo and Vegan Pumpkin Spice Creamer
des: "The perfect creamer for fall! All of the good stuff and none of the fake stuff! Keeps in the refrigerator for one week."
ins: Whisk coconut milk, pumpkin puree, maple syrup, flax milk, and pumpkin pie spice together in a bowl; pour into a mason jar or container with a lid. Cover and gently shake before using. Store in refrigerator.
